    "en": {
      "title": "Detention of Indian fishermen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mannar Magistrate yesterday (21) ordered that the 6 Rameswara fishermen who were arrested for trespassing in Sri Lankan waters and engaged in fishing should be remanded until the next 4th.",
        "The Sri Lankan Navy arrested a fishing boat from Rameswaram last Wednesday (20) and 6 fishermen on board for catching fish across the border and took them to the Thalaimannar Naval Camp for investigation.",
        "Following the investigations, the marines handed over to Mannar District Maritime Department officials in the afternoon.",
        "After investigations, the officials of the Maritime Industry Department appeared before the Mannar Magistrate in the Mannar Court yesterday (21) evening.",
        "During this, the Mannar Magistrate who conducted the investigations ordered the said 6 Indian fishermen to be remanded till the next 4th. (a)"
      ],
